      <li class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">National Society of Genetic Counselors: Find a Genetic Counselor. <a href="https://findageneticcounselor.nsgc.org/" class="text-sky-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">nsgc.org ↗</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>`;

const p5 = s['patient-p5'] || `
<div class="space-y-5 text-[0.92rem] text-slate-600 leading-[1.75]">
  <p>For the first time in history, we are moving from simply understanding ADLD to actively treating it. The ADLD Center is driving several groundbreaking initiatives to find a cure.</p>
