      <p class="text-slate-500 text-[0.88rem] leading-relaxed">Post-mortem brain donation is one of the most profound gifts a family can give to science. Brain tissue allows researchers to uncover exactly how ADLD destroys myelin and test new therapies on human tissue. If you are interested in registering as a donor, please contact the ADLD Center to coordinate with our tissue bank partners.</p>
